flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: New supplier or product master record creation OR shipment created OR periodic re-screening/regulation update]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest supplier, product, shipment, license docs, and regulatory feeds into platform]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS - Normalize and enrich master data, map tentative HS/INCOTERM candidates, compute preliminary risk attributes]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: Remote Functions - Execute screening and license validation calls; compute composite risk score and deterministic rule outcomes]
  N3 --> N4{PB: Process Builder & CWB Lifecycle - Evaluate against guardrails in Process Builder rules; auto-confirm low-risk master data and auto-approve shipments or create CWB for exceptions}
  N4 -->|Primary| N5[PB: Remote Functions - Writeback confirmed master data and license status to S4 and trigger shipment release or hold]
  N5 --> N6[PB: UI Screen & Notification - Surface exceptions and provide reviewers with UI Screen and attach documents; send notifications to stakeholders]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Higher compliance coverage and accuracy (reduced violations), improved duty/tax treatment accuracy lowering COGS, faster license-to-ship cycles and supplier onboarding, fewer manual reviews for low-risk cases, auditable decision trail.]
  N4 -->|Screening result = denied match or co...| B1[Create CWB Lifecycle exception for compliance review; block shipment; request supplemental documents and escalate to legal]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Shipment held, human review ensures no prohibited activity; auditable case created]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|HS code mapping ambiguous or multiple...| B2[Set product master state to 'tentative', create Process Builder Action Item for trade data steward to resolve with UI Screen supporting document attachments]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Avoid incorrect duty treatment while allowing onboarding to continue under watch; decision recorded]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Valid license present and risk score ...| B3[Auto-confirm master data, auto-approve shipment, writeback license metadata to S4 and mark CWB not required]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Faster license-to-ship cycle and reduced manual workload]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]